Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:25.41,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Whatever they decide, Applebloom, we'll be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:26.38,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.63,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Even though it could change everything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.61,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.23,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.92,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,We here have decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:58.50,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,That you're old enough stay home alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.41,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,and take care of the chores yourself for the afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.99,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I accept your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.39,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Staying home alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.04,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,By myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,On my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.86,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I am really doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now hey there, filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know you're excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:33.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but being the only pony here to take care of the day's chores is a big responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.14,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:38.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And it means everything to me that y'all think I am grown up enough to handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.71,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:43.60,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Well, if'n I wanna make my train, I best to be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:49.65,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,When grandaunt Pineapple says a pony's got to arrive by a certain time you'd better be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:52.86,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,You be sure and take care now, Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.21,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Y'all take care as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.36,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,I don't know which of your delivery routes is tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.91,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,You're each headed to a mighty hard to reach town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:04.45,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.74,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We know, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:09.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I agreed to let Applebloom stay behind alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.45,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:13.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't mean it like that, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's just I take my job as your big sister real serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Which is why I spent all night making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.11,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just a little list of helpful reminders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,There's some soup for you in the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.15,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Be sure to not heat it up too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.28,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If it's hot, blow on it to cool it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.62,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And take little sips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If you gulp, you could get hiccups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.76,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You don't to have worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.02,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And the chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I am ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I am just not so sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:47.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But, you trust me and believe I am grown up enough to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:52.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Good luck, little sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Okay! Great! See you soon! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See you later, little sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.77,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,See ya! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.17,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Yeeeeaaap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I am alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,At home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I am home alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Big Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I was just fretting a bit about Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You think she is going to be okay on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:45.87,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:50.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just keep on thinking of things I forgot to put on her list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:53.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Like, I didn't write down that if she wants to get a spoon out of the drawer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,she needs to open the drawer first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know I am probably just being silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.37,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:05.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But I know I'd feel a heap better if I could just check on Applebloom one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead and make your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna take a quick peek and then I'll make mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:24.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Okay, number one seventy two. "Make sure to pump the bellows to keep the stove warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.88,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,"Make sure the hats and bows closet is fully stocked."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,That's everything on Applejack's list!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:43.61,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And now that my chores are done, since there's no-one else here, I get to make all of the decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:48.41,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If I wanna listen to music, I can! If I wanna read a book, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:52.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If I just wanna stand here in the kitchen talkin' to myself, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Applebloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:04.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I came back to check on you, and I'm so glad I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I never thought about how dangerous things are round here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.82,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I'm really gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You are now! Because I'm here and I'm stayin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:21.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No way am I leavin' my little baby sister home alone all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm not a baby! I can take care of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.04,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And what about those pies you're supposed to deliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:31.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Pies? Ha, family's way more important than pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine! And, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.86,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This was kind of your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:41.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know. I should never have left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:48.28,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But I don't need you looking after me. I'm perfectly capable of stayin' home alone. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:54.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just look! "There's some soup for you in the refrigerator."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This is worse than I thought! Well don't worry, Applebloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:11.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm here now and I'm not leavin' you home alone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm stickin' right by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,always!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:26.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Applebloom? Applebloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.25,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack's just overreactin' a bit. I'm sure she'll snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You need somethin'? I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know you mean well, but I don't need you watchin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can take care of things myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.91,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who put pillows on this rake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:58.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know. Maybe someone who really loves her little sister and doesn't want her to get an owie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:08.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hey, Applejack! Watch me buck these apples on my own without anythin' bad happenin' to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,For the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You've gone and baby-proofed everythin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yup! Your big sister let you down once,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but I promise it won't ever happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:58.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But really, I'm fine! I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.80,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't need you watchin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:06.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's sweet! I appreciate you tryin' to make me feel better, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:10.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll always be here for you. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason I asked y'all to come over quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hey Applebloom! You need anything? A snack? A hoof massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe a snack while havin' a hoof massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.15,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Why that sounds delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.99,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:31.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,O-kay, well you can count on me bein' close by if'n you need anythin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:36.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean? If this keeps up, I'm never gonna be able to do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.45,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,anythin' without Applejack hoverin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.33,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.91,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,The pies! I'll sneak out and deliver them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.28,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Granny said they were goin' to some incredibly hard to reach town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:06.21,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If I can do it alone, that'll show Applejack I don't need somepony watchin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.80,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Just one problem. Your sister's gonna come back and check on you any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.58,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Which means you need an escape plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.73,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And I got an idea for one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.81,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,See? It'll look just like you're sleeping in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.58,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Sweetie and I can take turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:35.93,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That way, when one of us gets tired, the other can take over. Brilliant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You know what? It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I got a feelin' this just might work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:47.06,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make my sister see \N    I don't need her watchin' over me-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.46,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,No time for a song! Applejack's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.59,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna go we've gotta get you out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Everythin' okay in there, Sugarcube?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.87,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Quick, get in while I hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.06,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Sweetie, no! You gotta sleep like Applebloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.37,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,How does she sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.84,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Like she does everything! With sass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:41.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess you must've been so tuckered out you sent your friends home and went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Then again, you are a delicate flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sleep tight, Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll check on you again in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just checkin' in on you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Need anythin' now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How 'bout now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Need another blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Did I hear a cough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Want a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just... checkin' in on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Look at you, dozin' so peaceful-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:35.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Here I am, checkin' up on you every five seconds, and you're totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:39.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't need me frettin' over you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Wow, Applebloom will be so glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Huh? Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.61,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,N-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle? But... where's Applebloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She could be anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:13:00.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She could be lost, cold, hungry, itchy, stuffed up, needin' to go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we know exactly where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:05.67,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's making your pie delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Didn't she hear how difficult and dangerous it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:16.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I may never see my little sister again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay, Rarity's on her way over to look after you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now tell me, did Applebloom at least bring flame-proof boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A lion-tamer's chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A snake charmin' flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A hunk of ricotta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe there's still time to catch her before she gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,When did she leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.23,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It must've been hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:21.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't see a darn thing in this swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.62,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, now at least I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:56.68,Tiger,,0,0,0,,I'd stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.54,Tiger,,0,0,0,,This is the the only safe spot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.10,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It don't look so safe to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.67,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Oh, we just mean from the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.20,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.20,Snake,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.06,Snake,,0,0,0,,Oh, can you guys speak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:22.89,Tiger,,0,0,0,,I was about to tell our guest how we haven't eat in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:26.34,Sheep,,0,0,0,,My sister and I can never agree what to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.42,Snake,,0,0,0,,Except… pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:39.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well… Unfortunately I gotta get these pies to a town on the other side of swamp, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.10,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.94,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You don't need to worry about anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:52.73,Snake,,0,0,0,,Because we are going to have our apple pie with a side of filly filet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You don't say?…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.79,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Now, sisters, on three
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.94,Tiger,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.85,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.28,Snake,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:26.92,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.58,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you are going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.49,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Where are the pies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.41,Snake,,0,0,0,,They are not back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.14,Sheep,,0,0,0,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.49,Sheep,,0,0,0,,You think you've always gotta be in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.00,Tiger,,0,0,0,,Oh… You are lucky you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:34.27,Tiger,,0,0,0,,You've got no idea what it's like to have a sister constantly looking over your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.35,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh… Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.06,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Let's try listening a me for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:45.28,Sheep,,0,0,0,,And I say. If there are no pies, let's settle for the filly filet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:50.74,Snake,,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.88,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I really wish my sister were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Applebloom! I'm a-comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.89,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Hey! I thought I was in charge now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Howdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.81,Sheep,,0,0,0,,Ricotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:14.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.37,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I told you you need your big sister looking after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad this wasn't a whole lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure we lost the cart, and all the pies, but at least you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:45.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Huh, the cart! And all the pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You actually got them all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,In the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Through the flame geyser swamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Past that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well… yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Huh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's mighty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Anypony who can do that on her own, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,she don't need somepony like me babyin' her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.45,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, glee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,This pie's even tastier than my momma's swampwater casserole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Aw, now momma don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:42.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just remember you fellers wouldn't be enjoyin' these pies if it weren't for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.77,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:50.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But this don't change the fact that tryin' to make this delivery on your own was a plum-crazy thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Huh, I bet Granny Smith grounds you for a month for sneakin' out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:21:00.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And if Big Mac, Granny Smith 'n I ever have to be away for the day again…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:06.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I would totally trust you to stay home and take care of things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess I did get a little carried away  watching over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:15.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and if you hadn't snuck out like you did, maybe I wouldn't have figured that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:21.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Now that is the kind of 'looking after me' that I can definitely appreciate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,So… we're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Little sister, we're always good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
